name: Cute Black Gerber Daisy Flower with Green Nylon Headband
description: Looking for non-traditional girl bows to dress up you little one in. I carry all the colors you don't normally see on girls. I attached a small piece of velcro if you would like to place the flower alone in the hair. The headband is nylon and stretchy. All my items are interchangeable. Thanks for Looking!
